item.content:
&lt;p class=&quot;ng-binding&quot;&gt;The ginga (pronounced jeen-gah) is the fundamental footwork of capoeira. Its constant triangular footwork makes capoeira easily recognizable as well as confusing since it looks much more like a rhythmic dance step than an orthodox static fighting stance.&lt;/p&gt;
